-- Eni Says It's Starting Oil Production at Onshore Arcadia Field in Egypt
-- Tommaso Ebhardt
-- 2010-07-28T08:06:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-28/eni-says-it-s-starting-oil-production-at-onshore-arcadia-field-in-egypt.html

          
          
             Eni SpA said today in an e-mailed
statement that it started oil production at the Arcadia field in
Egypt.  
 To fully develop the field, four more wells will be drilled
in 2010 and 2011, to produce as much as 3,000 barrels of oil
equivalent a day, according to the statement.  
          
          


  


        